name: Leap of Faith (itch) (Quasarc)
description:
Move with Arrow keys or WASD.

Collect all checkpoints to progress! You can bounce on enemies, but not for long.

Most levels have a shortcut to save time. Can you find them all?

Online leaderboards: compete to be the fastest!

SFXs from Mixkit.co and Pixabay.com.
